Read about hexadecimal system.
Number system conversions:
1. 0x1AF -> binary = 0001 1010 1111
2. 11011110 -> hex = 0xDE
3. 0x8E -> binary = 1000 1110
4. 31,301 -> hex = 0x7A45
31,301mod16 = 5
1956mod16 = 4
122mod16 = 10
7

5. 0x2F + 0x5C -> hex = 0x8B
